https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/Sub-P,String,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/P1,,Sub-P,,,REGEX(202.*)
https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/Sub-R,Relationship,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/R1,,urn:ngsi-ld:relationships:Sub-R,,,REGEX(202.*)
https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/Sub-P2,String,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/P2,,Sub-P2,,,REGEX(202.*)
https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/Sub-R2,Relationship,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/R2,,urn:ngsi-ld:relationships:Sub-R2,,,REGEX(202.*)


06. Append P1 and R3 with noOverwrite set (P1 will be ignored as it already existed)
====================================================================================
HTTP/1.1 207 Multi Status
Content-Length: 211
Content-Type: application/json
Link: <https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/v1/ngsi-ld-core-context.jsonld>; rel="http://www.w3.org/ns/json-ld#context"; type="application/ld+json"
