Append,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/R2,Relationship,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,t,,,urn:ngsi-ld:relationships:R2,,,REGEX(202.*)
Append,https://uri.etsi.org/ngsi-ld/default-context/R3,Relationship,urn:ngsi-ld:entities:E1,t,,,urn:ngsi-ld:relationships:R3,,,REGEX(202.*)


09. See the sub-attributes in the temporal database
===================================================
id,valuetype,entityid,attributeid,unitcode,text,number,boolean,ts
